{
  "texts": [
    "Users can recreate several behaviors that are similar to our everyday activities in the Metaverse because it is a simulation of the real world.",
    "Socializing, having fun, and exchanging are just a few of these activities.",
    "The facilitation of a common currency may be necessary for all of these activities, and this can be done by using cryptographic assets.",
    "This cryptocurrency can be used by Metaverse users to pay for digital goods and services in both the real world and the virtual world (Gadekallu et al. 2022).",
    "The significant role that blockchain has played in the emergence of the Metaverse is examined in (Ning et al. 2021) about the governmental and commercial spheres, while its potential application for VR object connection is stated."
  ]
}